flowchart TD
    Start([GitHub Action Triggered]) --> CheckConditions

    subgraph Step 1: Check Conditions
        CheckConditions{Event Type}
        CheckConditions -->|workflow_dispatch / call| SetDefault[run=true<br/>agent=cogni-ai-architect]
        CheckConditions -->|issue / discussion / comment| CommentCheck{Check Role & Mentions}
        CheckConditions -->|pull_request / PR target| PRCheck{Check Role}

        CommentCheck -->|Review Trigger| SetReviewer[run=true<br/>agent=cogni-ai-reviewer]
        CommentCheck -->|Standard Trigger| SetParsed[run=true<br/>agent=Parsed from Body]
        CommentCheck -->|No Match| Skip[run=false]

        PRCheck -->|Allowed Role| SetDefaultPR[run=true<br/>agent=cogni-ai-architect]
        PRCheck -->|Not Allowed| Skip

        SetDefault --> FinalAgent[Output: run & effective_agent]
        SetReviewer --> FinalAgent
        SetParsed --> FinalAgent
        SetDefaultPR --> FinalAgent
        Skip --> FinalAgent
    end

    FinalAgent --> ShouldRun{run == 'true'?}
    ShouldRun -->|No| EndSkipped([End - Action Skipped])
    ShouldRun -->|Yes| WaitConcurrency

    subgraph Step 2: Prepare Environment
        WaitConcurrency[Wait for Concurrent Runs] --> |Polls GitHub API| ResolvePrompt
        ResolvePrompt[Resolve Prompt] --> |Builds Prompt text<br/>adds Re-run notes| Checkout
        Checkout[Clone Dependencies] --> |clones agents, instructions, skills| ConvertPerms
        ConvertPerms[Convert Permissions] --> |Merges default & agent perms| RunOpenCode
    end

    subgraph Step 3: Agent Execution
        RunOpenCode[Run anomalyco/opencode]
        RunOpenCode -->|Executes configured agent| EvaluateResult
    end

    subgraph Step 4: Post-Run
        EvaluateResult{Response exists?}
        EvaluateResult -->|Yes| WriteSummary[Write to Step Summary]
        EvaluateResult -->|No| CheckFailure
        WriteSummary --> CheckFailure

        CheckFailure{Job Failed or Cancelled?}
        CheckFailure -->|Yes| PrintLogs[Print OpenCode Logs]
        CheckFailure -->|No| End([End])
        PrintLogs --> End
    end
